description:
Mô Tả Công Việc


              At Navigos, we are focused on mastering employment and evaluation. This year, we are launching new businesses in HR field to bring more values to customers in Vietnam.


              As a business development executive to a new business, you will be responsible for the following:

              1. Work on the development of  the new business;

              - Identify the market for a new product and understand target customers;

              - Find the key selling points and utilize them in presenting the product to customers;

              - Support product team by continuously collecting and sharing customers’ feedback;

              - Assist the team with problem definition and product refinement.

              2. Build and follow the sales process for a new product ;

              - Find leads, set up  an appointment to meet potential clients and understand their needs;

              - Establish relations with the new clients that build  trust needed to be able to sell the product;

              - Once sales is made, provide after sales support to ensure excellent service and to collect useful feedback.

              3. Continuously follow up with existing clients and leads.

              4. Prepare business development plan by carrying out research, market analysis to win new customers and expand market share & grow company’s revenue.

              5. Achieve the assigned target and performance goals.

              6. Accept other given duties and involve in projects assigned by CGO (Chief Growth Officer and the Management).


              Xem toàn bộ Mô Tả Công Việc

requirement:
Yêu Cầu Công Việc


              We are looking forward to hearing from those with:

              - University Degree, English – working proficiency, and Computer literate;

              - From 2 years as a senior sales/Business development/ Project leader or similar position (experience in HR industry will be a plus) ;

              - Experience to meet directly with clients to communicate, negotiate and close the deal;

              - Strong passion for New business/Startups, and creating things that can impact and make more value for HR field.

              - Can-do attitude;

              - Interpersonal and Analytical skills;

              - Negotiation and Problem solving skills.


              Xem toàn bộ Yêu Cầu Công Việc
